OL,3,CSparks fly as smash-and-grab-thieves
OL,4,Crip cashpoint from shop in string of
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,FThe brazen tactics of a pair of
OL,8,Fthieves who targeted a string of
OL,9,Fbusinesses in the South East have been
OL,10,Fexposed in CCTV which shows angle
OL,11,Fgrinders and 4x4s used to break into
OL,12,Fshops.
OL,14,FVideo released by Surrey Police shows
OL,15,Fsparks fly as a security barrier is
OL,16,Fcut, a car smashing through doors and
OL,17,Feven a cashpoint pulled out of a shop.
