OL,3,CSparks fly as smash-and-grab-thieves
OL,4,Crip cashpoint from shop in string of
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,FDuring one raid in Sussex a crowbar
OL,8,Fwas thrown at officers before the pair
OL,9,Ftried to make a quick getaway with
OL,10,Ftheir boot open sending stolen goods
OL,11,Fflying across the road.
OL,13,FDean Beldom from Burnham in
OL,14,FBuckinghamshire and his brother Andrew
OL,15,FSmith from New Haw in Surrey were
OL,16,Fsentenced to six years and six months
OL,17,Frespectively after police caught up
OL,18,Fwith their crime spree "driven
OL,19,Fentirely by greed."
