OL,7,FInvestigating officer Sergeant Sarah
OL,8,FWentworth added: "They showed no
OL,9,Fremorse and no regard for the damage
OL,10,Fcaused or the risk posed to others as
OL,11,Fwell as a blatant disregard for the
OL,12,Fcriminal justice system.
OL,14,F"I would like to thank everyone who
OL,15,Fhas contributed to this investigation
OL,16,Ffor helping to put these men behind
OL,17,Fbars where they belong."
